<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>FIND MY BUS</title>
    <style>
        .right1{
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-left: 50px;
            width: 35%;
            border: 3px ;
            padding: 80px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            background-color:#ffd6ff;
            padding-top: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-right: 150px;
        }
        .right2{
            padding: 80px;
            background-color:#ffd6ff;
            width: 40%;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body style="background-color:#c8b6ff;">
    <div>
        <form action="/auth2/bus" method="post">
            <div class="right1" style="align-items: center;float:left">
            <h2 style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:0px" >Search Bus  
            <i class="bi bi-bus-front"></i> </h2><br>
            <label for="from"  style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:20px">From 
                <input type="text" name="from" id="text" style="border-radius: 20px;" width="20px" height="20px">
            </label><br><br>
            <label for="to" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:20px">  To              
                <input type="text" name="to" id="text" style="border-radius: 20px;" width="20px" height="20px">
            <br>
            <br><p><button type="submit" style="background-color: black;color:aliceblue">
                    Search
            </button></p>
            </div>
        </form>
        <div class="right2" style="float:left">
                <form action="/auth2/bus" method="post">
                    <h2 style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:0px" >Book Tickets <i class="bi bi-ticket-perforated"></i></h2><br>
                    <label for="from" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:30px">  From              
                    <input type="text" name="from" id="text" style="border-radius: 20px;" width="20px" height="20px">
                    <br></label><br><br>
                <label for="to" style="font-family: Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif;padding-left:30px">  To              
                    <input type="text" name="to" id="text" style="border-radius: 20px;" width="20px" height="20px">
                <br></label><br>
                <br><p><button type="submit" style="background-color: black;color:aliceblue">
                    Book
                </button></p><br>
                </form>
                <p>
                    <h4>How to book ticket?</h4>
                    1.ENTER YOUR FROM AND TO PLACE
                    <br>
                    2.DOUBLE CLICK THE BOOK OR SEARCH BUTTON
                    <br>
                    3.CHOOSE YOUR BUS
                    <br>
                    4.BOOK YOUR TICKET
                    <br>
                    5.TICKET SEND TO YOUR MAIL
                </p>
        </div><br>
    </div>

</body>
</html>